com.agorapulse.micronaut.aws.dynamodb.annotation

Annotation Type HashKey


  • @Inherited
 @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={PARAMETER,ANNOTATION_TYPE})
public @interface HashKey
    Annotates hash key. This annotation is not required if the name of the argument contains word hash.
